    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving masterpiece. Powered by the S54 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, it delivers linear power through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, while the variable M differential lock ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul, ensuring the drivetrain operates at peak thermal efficiency. A true driver's spec with excellent mechanical feedback and visceral performance.",
