      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a dependable new-to-you ride? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super reliable for me, always well-maintained, and it still drives like a dream. It's got plenty of life left and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
