    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels through a variable M differential lock. The chassis dynamics are sharp, benefiting from a balanced 50/50 weight distribution and a responsive steering rack. Key mechanical preventative measures have been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS service and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring the structural integrity matches the engine's performance. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a driven enthusiast car, the mechanical components remain robust, offering the visceral feedback and linear power delivery this chassis is renowned for.",
